<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>هـ د د<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٣٧٠ - هـ د د]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هَدَّ٢ هَدَدْتُ، يَهِدّ، اهْدِدْ/ هِدَّ، هَدًّا وهديدًا، فهو هِدّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• هَدَّ الحائطُ ونحوُه:</span> سقط.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• هَدَّ الشَّخصُ:</span> ضعُف وهرِم <span class="c1">"ظلَّ يعمل إلى أن هدَّ"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>